00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:56.710
Point means that you cannot find a

00:21:56.720 --> 00:21:59.190
better run in the sense that it is going

00:21:59.200 --> 00:22:02.710
to be both higher score and faster to

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:05.430
train and the set of parito points is

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:07.470
called the parito front you kind of can

00:22:07.480 --> 00:22:10.510
draw a curve through uh that set of

00:22:10.520 --> 00:22:12.190
points and how much time you have to

00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:14.909
